{"tid":2025120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對付藍絲，最有效係用”愛國不愛黨” 屌返佢唔愛國","createTime":"2020-05-20T04:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T07:28:02.000Z","uid":244332,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"712f2d99ece81ddef7f3533671a82ce6c3f993cd","tid":2025120,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"雖然自己信念唔係&rdquo;愛國不愛黨&rdquo;, 支那唔代表我<br />\n<br />\n但對付藍絲，如果你認係港獨份子，你講咩都冇用<br />\n<br />\n用&rdquo;愛國不愛黨&rdquo;，<span style=\"color: red;\">屌返佢唔愛國，迫佢think out of the box突破佢思維</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=藍絲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=黃絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你港獨曱甴，幫美國佬搞亂中國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我愛中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你為左共產黨利益出賣中國人，你愧對中國人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下 即係點？？？我中立，我係為中國好....<br />\n<br />\n（下省一千字講述共產黨點害中國）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：賣國賊，你為貪官利益 出賣中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你助紂為虐，你係咪想害死中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔配做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16151497f2d82b411615fd3fa15cf8e5ac47407d","tid":2025120,"uid":56147,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"試下再跳脫d   申明自己愛黨唔愛國   所以xxxxx  e.g 贊成日本侵華   贊成割地比蘇聯  愛美國因為黨幹好多美國人"},{"pid":"d068191e7fd01257c99659ce5bc9dcc7ede0152a","tid":2025120,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:01:58.000Z",